title: Umphrey's McGee Covers the World 1998 - 2013
description:
Umph Love! 

For you listening pleasure here are the vast majority of songs that Umphrey's has covered over their career.

Hours, days, probably weeks of work has gone into searching out and compiling these 567 different covers from 1989 to 2013!

All soundboard recordings arranged by year and tagged properly with source. Categorized between jams, mashups and acoustic covers, including the "Cover It" releases. 

Don't download and dash, it's not cool. 
Share your coments and corrections or additons too 

2014 covers will be posted at the end of the year (if I feel the love)

Enjoy,

Dubble D
